<div class='panel'><h2>Code of Conduct</h2>

<b>NOTE: these are initial and subject to change</b>

<ul>
<li>Anyone is welcome to open an account either as your personal account, or to run a bot. Open as many bot accounts as you like.</li>
<li>If you run a bot here, please be kind to the servers. If the instance starts to bog down, bots that are making lots of API calls will get shut down.</li>
<li>Do not use bots to abuse users. <a href="https://www.crummy.com/2013/11/27/0">Bots should punch up</a>, not down.</li>
</ul>

<p>
If you have questions or concerns, feel free to contact me at <a href="https://mastodon.social/@muffinista">muffinista@mastodon.social</a>, <a href="https://twitter.com/muffinista">@muffinista</a> on twitter, or by emailing <code>colin at muffinlabs.com</code></p></div>
